 human redemption.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aFiction. 4aGeneral. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aFinney, Ernest J., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000z97831106353480 cprintz978052021638940uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052035389340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520353893423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520353893/original  a978-3-11-063534-8  University of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles